snippet.title: Barely Racing Trailer 2023
snippet.description:
We are proud to present trailer for our new game. Expected release is by the end of this year. 

Do you like what you see? Wishlist the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1351480/Barely_Racing/
Do you want to try out the game? Follow this link: https://www.fragile-software.com/apply-for-beta/
